data.description: Stunning home on a lake in the Country Club of Miami / Town of Miami Lakes area. This beautiful home has 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths, volume ceilings, lots of natural light, screened patio, split floor plan, & 1 car garage. Each bathroom has both a tub & shower, with new light fixtures & toilets. Primary bathroom has a large Roman tub & shower, dual sinks in vanity, & skylight above the large Roman tub. The bedroom at the front entrance was converted during the original construction to a den with a wet bar. It can be restored as a bedroom by removing the wet bar area & reinstalling the closet. House has a new central HVAC system, new electric wiring & new breaker box. Ceramic tile throughout, with laminate wood flooring in bedrooms. A perfect blend of luxury and natural beauty!
